                Oh no! Looks like there's a break in the chain!                 
                                                                                
        Beads is using embedded dolt mode, which takes an exclusive lock        
        on the database. Perles needs server mode for concurrent access.        
                                                                                
                   Re-initialize your project in server mode:                   
                                                                                
